    <title></title>
    <url>/2023/02/16/%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="动态规划部分"><a href="#动态规划部分" class="headerlink" title="动态规划部分"></a>动态规划部分</h1><h2 id="背包问题："><a href="#背包问题：" class="headerlink" title="背包问题："></a>背包问题：</h2><p>1.<strong>01背包</strong>：f(i)(j)表示从前i个物品里面选取不超过重量为j的物品所获得的最大价值，状态转移方程为:f(i)(j)&#x3D;max(f(i-1)(j),f(i-1)(j-w(i))+v(i)).</p>
<p>2.**完全背包 **：在01背包的基础上，每个物品的选择次数没有限制，状态转移方程为：f(i)(j)&#x3D;max(f(i-1)(j),f(i)(j-w[i])+v[i]) <em><strong>意思就是要么第i个物品一个都不选，要么就选一个，然后继续试探能否再选。</strong></em></p>
<p>3.**多重背包 **：没掌握住QAQ,<a href="https://www.luogu.com.cn/problem/P1077">但可以参考这个题，也是不同类型的物品，有不同的数量</a>。</p>
<p><strong>注意</strong>：</p>
<p>01背包是从最大容量开始往前递推，即第二层循环为for(int j&#x3D;m;j&gt;&#x3D;0;j–) *<font color="#dd0000">（不要看学习通上的那个代码）</font>*。</p>
<hr>
<h1 id="图论"><a href="#图论" class="headerlink" title="图论"></a>图论</h1><h3 id="I-存图方式："><a href="#I-存图方式：" class="headerlink" title="I.存图方式："></a>I.存图方式：</h3><p>1.邻接矩阵：**<font color="Red">缺点就是不能构建重边，且占用内存较大</font> **</p>
<figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> u,v,w;<span class="comment">//&quot;u,v&quot; meanings the beginning and end of a edge,&quot;W&quot;meanings the assignment of this edge.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> map[N][N];</span><br><span class="line">cin&gt;&gt;u&gt;&gt;v&gt;&gt;w;</span><br><span class="line">map[u][v]=map[v][u]=w;<span class="comment">//connect the edge and give it assignment.</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<p>2.邻接表</p>
<figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title class_">edge</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> v,w;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;<span class="comment">//Considering that we need to store the end point that connecting to this point and the assignment of the edge built by these two points &quot;u,v&quot;,so we use &quot;struct&quot; to be the data type of &quot;vector&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">vector&lt;edge&gt;e[N];</span><br><span class="line">cin&gt;&gt;u&gt;&gt;v&gt;&gt;w;</span><br><span class="line">e[u].<span class="built_in">push_back</span>(&#123;v,w&#125;);</span><br><span class="line">e[v].<span class="built_in">push_back</span>(&#123;u,w&#125;);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<p>3.<strong><font color="Green"> 链式前向星</font></strong>(目前还没有掌握住)</p>
<hr>
<h2 id="II-计算最短路径的方法："><a href="#II-计算最短路径的方法：" class="headerlink" title="II.计算最短路径的方法："></a>II.计算最短路径的方法：</h2><p>1.floyd算法：</p>
<figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> f[N][N];<span class="comment">//array&quot;f&quot; meanings the shortest length of two points;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> INF=<span class="number">0x3f3f3f3f</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title class_">edge</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> v,w;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;node[N];</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">cin&gt;&gt;u&gt;&gt;v&gt;&gt;w;</span><br><span class="line">e[u].<span class="built_in">push_back</span>(&#123;v,w&#125;);</span><br><span class="line">e[v].<span class="built_in">push_back</span>(&#123;u,w&#125;);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> i=<span class="number">1</span>;i&lt;=n;i++)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    f[i][i]=<span class="number">0</span>;<span class="comment">//自己到自己的距离为0</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> j=<span class="number">1</span>;j&lt;=n;j++)</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span>(j==i||e[i].v==j)<span class="keyword">continue</span>;<span class="comment">//如果是自己或者是和自己相连的点，就跳过。</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span> f[i][j]=INF;<span class="comment">//不相连的话两者距离就为正无穷。</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">/*The template:*/</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> k=<span class="number">1</span>;k&lt;=n;k++)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> i=<span class="number">1</span>;i&lt;=n;i++)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> j=<span class="number">1</span>;j&lt;=n;j++)</span><br><span class="line">            f[i][j]=<span class="built_in">min</span>(f[i][j],f[i][k]+f[k][j]);</span><br><span class="line">            </span><br><span class="line">            </span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<hr>
<hr>
<p>2.dijkstra算法：</p>
<figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title class_">edge</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="type">int</span> v, w;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">vector&lt;edge&gt; e[maxn];</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> dis[maxn], vis[maxn],INF=<span class="number">0x3f3f3f3f</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title">dijkstra</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">int</span> n, <span class="type">int</span> s)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="built_in">memset</span>(dis, INF, <span class="built_in">sizeof</span>(dis));</span><br><span class="line">  dis[s] = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> i = <span class="number">1</span>; i &lt;= n; i++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> u = <span class="number">0</span>, mind = <span class="number">0x3f3f3f3f</span>;<span class="comment">//由于每一次都要从里起点最近的点出发寻找，所以最外层的循环需要来做这一层工作。</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> j = <span class="number">1</span>; j &lt;= n; j++)</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">if</span> (!vis[j] &amp;&amp; dis[j] &lt; mind) u = j, mind = dis[j];<span class="comment">//如果这个点没有被访问，且小于mind(第一次的时候就是表示找到了起点，然后起点到自己的距离又为0，故不会被覆盖。往后就是，如果与前一个点相连接，然后记录两点距离mind，重复寻找并覆盖，找到最小的)</span></span><br><span class="line">    vis[u] = <span class="literal">true</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">auto</span> ed : e[u]) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="type">int</span> v = ed.v, w = ed.w;<span class="comment">//从上面找到的点寻找出度点，并更新起点到这个点的最短距离。</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">if</span> (dis[v] &gt; dis[u] + w) dis[v] = dis[u] + w;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//优先队列优化做法：</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>





<p><strong>注意</strong>：1.无穷大的表示为<font color="Blue"> max&#x3D;0x3f3f3f3f</font>,无穷小表示为<font color="Blue">min&#x3D;0xc0c0c0c0</font></p>
]]></content>
